WEBVTT

00:00:20.180 --> 00:00:21.290
(Shen Jibai,)

00:00:21.930 --> 00:00:23.890
(you are filled with so many secrets.)

00:00:24.340 --> 00:00:25.770
(After going through all of this,)

00:00:26.020 --> 00:00:28.250
(I finally know what
you were protecting back then.)

00:00:29.130 --> 00:00:30.660
(If I could go back to the past,)

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:33.100
(I wouldn't want
to be a person full of secrets.)

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:36.679
(Three months ago)

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:38.009
(The United Kingdom)

00:00:38.010 --> 00:00:42.649
This white-glazed
porcelain from the late Qing Dynasty.

00:00:42.650 --> 00:00:46.459
(Sotheby's Auction House)
It features a translucent sheen and intricate texture,

00:00:46.460 --> 00:00:48.520
showcasing masterful craftsmanship

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:51.040
(Mu Zhiyu, Heiress of Mu Group / Top Auctioneer)
and meticulous firing techniques.

00:00:51.040 --> 00:00:53.420
This is a Qianlong Imperial
fine-patterned white porcelain bowl.

00:00:53.930 --> 00:00:56.569
The current price is 22 million.

00:00:56.570 --> 00:00:58.370
Are there any higher bids?

00:00:59.420 --> 00:01:01.540
23 million sells it.

00:01:01.820 --> 00:01:04.100
23 million. Any further bids?

00:01:04.940 --> 00:01:09.329
23.5 million sells it.

00:01:09.330 --> 00:01:11.140
Are there any higher bids?

00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:14.650
Any higher bids?

00:01:21.580 --> 00:01:24.579
23.5 million.

00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:25.650
Last chance.

00:01:26.050 --> 00:01:28.650
(Shen Jibai, President of Security Group)
(Mu Zhiyu, we finally met.)

00:01:29.100 --> 00:01:31.370
(You will become my next mission.)

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.320
(Three hours ago)

00:01:35.540 --> 00:01:36.620
Shen Jibai,

00:01:37.130 --> 00:01:38.450
remember your mission.

00:01:39.490 --> 00:01:41.860
I will have you appointed
as the Mu family's head of security.

00:01:42.660 --> 00:01:43.980
Get close to Mu Zhiyu.

00:01:44.410 --> 00:01:47.500
Obtain the safe code
where her father keeps his inheritance,

00:01:47.770 --> 00:01:49.140
and I'll give you ten million.

00:01:52.940 --> 00:01:53.819
Deal.

00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:56.360
- It's a pleasure working with you.
- Pleasure is mine.

00:01:56.360 --> 00:01:57.800
(Xu Mingzhu, Vice President of Mu Group)

00:02:10.260 --> 00:02:11.850
Ruin tonight's auction.

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:12.650
Remember,

00:02:12.900 --> 00:02:13.900
don't hurt anyone.

00:02:15.900 --> 00:02:17.060
(Mu Zhiyu,)

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:18.460
(next,)

00:02:18.860 --> 00:02:21.370
(I will become your personal bodyguard.)

00:02:23.210 --> 00:02:24.180
Sold!

00:02:24.700 --> 00:02:28.500
- Someone is robbing us! Run!
- Someone is robbing us!

00:02:41.460 --> 00:02:42.530
Who are you?

00:02:44.930 --> 00:02:46.090
Don't make a sound.

00:03:06.070 --> 00:03:09.840
♪Ten years of the past
have turned to smoke♪

00:03:10.110 --> 00:03:13.400
♪I close my innocent eyes♪

00:03:13.450 --> 00:03:16.590
♪No more parting by life or death♪

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:20.260
♪Only mourning remains in my heart♪

00:03:22.040 --> 00:03:26.010
♪Deeply trapped
in a vortex of mysteries♪

00:03:26.100 --> 00:03:29.590
♪Wading through
the muddy waters of hearts and times♪

00:03:30.170 --> 00:03:33.529
♪Returning from the ashes
to craft the plan♪

00:03:33.530 --> 00:03:35.060
It's dangerous, don't move.

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:43.660
♪Love has vanished, hatred is spreading♪

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:48.589
♪Ignoring the arrangements of fate♪

00:03:48.590 --> 00:03:51.950
♪Only following my own will♪

00:03:54.070 --> 00:03:56.589
♪After a familiar embrace♪

00:03:56.590 --> 00:04:00.649
♪The world's turmoil
is still hard to discern♪

00:04:00.650 --> 00:04:02.609
♪The green flower breaks in two♪

00:04:02.610 --> 00:04:03.620
Are you okay?

00:04:05.180 --> 00:04:05.930
Here.

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:07.620
It's returned unharmed.

00:04:19.460 --> 00:04:20.490
Wait.

00:04:31.290 --> 00:04:33.089
Miss, Chairman Mu is hospitalized.

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:34.289
Are you returning home?

00:04:34.290 --> 00:04:35.140
Alright.

00:04:35.170 --> 00:04:36.220
I understand.

00:04:36.730 --> 00:04:38.700
I'll book a ticket
back home immediately.

00:04:47.060 --> 00:04:48.650
(Mu Zhiyu is returning home now.)

00:04:48.900 --> 00:04:50.380
(The plan officially begins.)

00:05:06.480 --> 00:05:11.309
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:05:11.310 --> 00:05:12.979
♪Because you exist♪

00:05:12.980 --> 00:05:15.059
♪You're always♪

00:05:15.060 --> 00:05:19.709
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:05:19.710 --> 00:05:22.339
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:05:22.340 --> 00:05:24.009
♪Hold tight♪

00:05:24.010 --> 00:05:29.799
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:05:29.800 --> 00:05:34.879
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 1=

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:36.619
(Domestic Nursing Home)
There are rumors

00:05:36.620 --> 00:05:39.459
that Mu Group President Mu Chenzhou
is in a coma after a stroke.

00:05:39.460 --> 00:05:40.939
Vice President Xu Mingzhu

00:05:40.940 --> 00:05:44.319
has refused to comment
on the rumors about her husband's health.

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:45.769
(Xu Mingzhu, Vice President of Mu Group)
She stated that the Mu Group's

00:05:45.770 --> 00:05:48.460
new auction will proceed as scheduled.

00:05:49.330 --> 00:05:50.260
Ms. Xu.

00:05:50.420 --> 00:05:52.940
(Mu Group Auction House)
Since Mr. Mu fell ill and was hospitalized,

00:05:52.940 --> 00:05:55.020
you have been handling
all the group's affairs.

00:05:55.210 --> 00:05:57.089
You are truly remarkable, Ms. Xu.

00:05:57.090 --> 00:05:58.260
Indeed.

00:05:58.410 --> 00:05:59.259
Ms. Xu,

00:05:59.260 --> 00:06:00.619
for this auction,

00:06:00.620 --> 00:06:02.849
you even managed
to get "Classic of Mountains and Seas"

00:06:02.850 --> 00:06:04.900
by the popular
Chinese-style artist, Hong.

00:06:05.020 --> 00:06:05.939
Mu Group

00:06:05.940 --> 00:06:09.020
really is the leading
auction company in the country.

00:06:09.820 --> 00:06:11.850
You two gentlemen flatter me too much.

00:06:12.020 --> 00:06:13.720
It's not just
"Classic of Mountains and Seas."

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:14.459
This time,

00:06:14.460 --> 00:06:17.649
I have also invited
a very formidable auctioneer.

00:06:17.650 --> 00:06:19.490
This will surely take the auction

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:20.849
to the next level.

00:06:20.850 --> 00:06:24.260
Don't worry, Ms. Xu,
there will be no problems.

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:26.560
(Jason, Auctioneer)
Regarding the opportunity you gave me,

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:28.020
I will definitely make the most of it.

00:06:28.460 --> 00:06:29.969
Next, please welcome

00:06:29.970 --> 00:06:32.769
the Mu Group's specially invited
award-winning auctioneer

00:06:32.770 --> 00:06:34.040
to the stage.

00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:37.960
(Moser International)

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:48.970
(How can it be her?)

00:06:49.730 --> 00:06:52.289
So the auctioneer invited by Ms. Xu

00:06:52.290 --> 00:06:53.699
is the daughter of the Mu family.

00:06:53.700 --> 00:06:54.579
I heard

00:06:54.580 --> 00:06:57.259
that Miss Mu was a leading auctioneer

00:06:57.260 --> 00:06:59.089
at Sotheby's in the UK.

00:06:59.090 --> 00:07:00.880
- Having her stay at Mu Group
- Hello everyone.

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.960
- is making the strong even stronger.
- I am Mu Zhiyu.

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:03.459
Next,

00:07:03.460 --> 00:07:06.610
I will introduce today's first exhibit,

00:07:07.170 --> 00:07:08.580
the Glazed Glass Lamp.

00:07:11.770 --> 00:07:12.819
The starting bid is

00:07:12.820 --> 00:07:13.730
8 million.

00:07:14.170 --> 00:07:15.610
The bidding starts now.

00:07:17.820 --> 00:07:18.780
9 million.

00:07:18.850 --> 00:07:20.379
9 million from this gentleman.

00:07:20.380 --> 00:07:21.379
10 million.

00:07:21.380 --> 00:07:23.290
- Why is Mu Zhiyu on the stage?
- 11 million.

00:07:23.290 --> 00:07:25.280
- Go find out where Jason is.
- Are there any higher bids?

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:26.490
11 million.

00:07:31.620 --> 00:07:32.490
Go check it out.

00:07:32.730 --> 00:07:33.649
11 million.

00:07:33.650 --> 00:07:34.530
Sold!

00:07:34.900 --> 00:07:37.900
(This Mu Zhiyu actually
has some tricks up her sleeve.)

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:43.460
(Don't get too ahead of yourself, brat.)

00:07:52.730 --> 00:07:54.220
It really has nothing to do with me!

00:07:54.260 --> 00:07:55.649
It's... It's Ms. Xu.

00:07:55.650 --> 00:07:57.089
She told me to work with a shill

00:07:57.090 --> 00:07:58.169
at the auction

00:07:58.170 --> 00:07:59.769
to drive the price up.

00:07:59.770 --> 00:08:01.849
So she could make
an under-the-table deal. It was her!

00:08:01.850 --> 00:08:02.939
Xu Mingzhu

00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.490
has gone crazy for money.

00:08:04.530 --> 00:08:06.170
By disrupting the auction like this,

00:08:06.290 --> 00:08:08.019
does she want to destroy Mu Group?

00:08:08.020 --> 00:08:08.940
He Min,

00:08:08.970 --> 00:08:10.490
thank you for your help this time.

00:08:11.140 --> 00:08:12.220
Zhiyu,

00:08:12.410 --> 00:08:13.619
as long as I can help you,

00:08:13.620 --> 00:08:14.780
I'll do anything.

00:08:14.820 --> 00:08:19.380
The next exhibit to be auctioned
is the final piece of this auction.

00:08:19.460 --> 00:08:22.619
At the same time,
it is the most anticipated one.

00:08:22.620 --> 00:08:23.499
It is...

00:08:23.500 --> 00:08:25.940
the new work by
the Chinese-style artist, Hong,

00:08:26.060 --> 00:08:28.020
"Classic of Mountains and Seas."

00:08:31.460 --> 00:08:33.080
The piece
"Classic of Mountains and Seas"

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:36.379
is taken from the ancient Qin record,
"Mythical Beasts in Classic of Mountains and Seas."

00:08:36.380 --> 00:08:37.580
The starting bid is

00:08:38.020 --> 00:08:39.259
12 million.

00:08:39.260 --> 00:08:40.820
The bidding starts now.

00:08:41.340 --> 00:08:42.700
13 million.

00:08:42.930 --> 00:08:44.490
15 million.

00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:45.689
16 million.

00:08:45.690 --> 00:08:48.449
16.5 million from this gentleman.
Would anyone like to bid higher?

00:08:48.450 --> 00:08:50.049
Are there any higher bids in the room?

00:08:50.050 --> 00:08:51.300
19 million.

00:08:53.410 --> 00:08:54.660
20 million.

00:08:54.930 --> 00:08:56.490
20 million.

00:08:59.930 --> 00:09:01.420
21 million.

00:09:02.290 --> 00:09:05.130
(She's playing a setup. Interesting.)

00:09:07.740 --> 00:09:09.420
22 million.

00:09:15.020 --> 00:09:15.979
(Stepmom,)

00:09:15.980 --> 00:09:17.540
(I'm going to make you
look like a fool.)

00:09:18.140 --> 00:09:19.379
22 million.

00:09:19.380 --> 00:09:20.379
Sold!

00:09:20.380 --> 00:09:23.409
Congratulations to
Ms. Xu Mingzhu of Mu Group

00:09:23.410 --> 00:09:25.289
for successfully bidding on Hong's

00:09:25.290 --> 00:09:26.490
"Classic of Mountains and Seas."

00:09:28.220 --> 00:09:29.610
Congratulations, Ms. Xu!

00:09:39.290 --> 00:09:40.420
Zhiyu...

00:09:46.220 --> 00:09:47.730
Welcome back.

00:09:48.930 --> 00:09:51.130
I wonder if you

00:09:51.220 --> 00:09:52.850
are satisfied with this gift?

00:09:52.980 --> 00:09:54.340
That's very thoughtful of you.

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:56.610
There's an even bigger surprise.

00:10:00.770 --> 00:10:01.689
Just now,

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:04.010
Ms. Xu and I reached an agreement.

00:10:04.220 --> 00:10:05.220
At this moment,

00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:06.619
I am not just here as

00:10:06.620 --> 00:10:09.169
the auctioneer
commissioned by Mu Group.

00:10:09.170 --> 00:10:10.090
At the same time,

00:10:10.290 --> 00:10:12.499
in my capacity
as the heiress of Mu Group,

00:10:12.500 --> 00:10:13.850
I announce this to everyone.

00:10:19.450 --> 00:10:20.569
Just now,

00:10:20.570 --> 00:10:23.130
the "Classic of Mountains and Seas"
acquired by Mu Group

00:10:23.140 --> 00:10:25.660
will be donated
to the Municipal Art Museum for free.

00:10:25.770 --> 00:10:26.770
Also,

00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:28.770
Mu Group hereby promises

00:10:29.020 --> 00:10:30.610
that the auction proceeds

00:10:30.650 --> 00:10:32.130
will be donated in their entirety.

00:10:33.500 --> 00:10:35.180
(You ruined my plan.)

00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:37.460
(I won't let you
have a good time either.)

00:10:37.530 --> 00:10:38.770
(As long as I'm here,)

00:10:38.930 --> 00:10:41.220
(don't even think
about coming for Mu Group.)

00:11:01.780 --> 00:11:06.010
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:11:06.150 --> 00:11:10.519
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:15.010
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:11:19.230 --> 00:11:23.169
♪Shadows move around♪

00:11:23.170 --> 00:11:27.779
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:11:27.780 --> 00:11:32.310
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:11:35.910 --> 00:11:41.700
♪Don't slip away♪

00:11:44.150 --> 00:11:48.719
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

